Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.41,0:00:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?你不做模特了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:08.81,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}本片字幕由異域字幕組(www.yydm.com)製作,僅供試看之用,如果喜歡本作品,請購買並支持正版!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我傷害了梅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:12.90,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻譯:梅子 熊貓  校對:小白 時間:果凍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我讓她很沒安全感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是大和今後會越來越紅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 從開始做模特時就沒想讓自己女朋友不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅對我才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要為了女朋友放棄自己的未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是在真心喜歡的人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的事就變得無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒有王子的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就不是王子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要梅看著我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:01:02.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday　言葉がたりなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:01:02.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日 言語不足以表達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:12.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すれ違ったとしても やめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:12.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使詞不達意 也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:19.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとわかりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:19.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:32.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時にひとりになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:32.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時 想一人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:44.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅をしても心は埋まらない そして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:44.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使旅行 內心的空虛也無法填補
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:49.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大切な人に気づくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:49.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我意識到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:53.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつもいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:53.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每時每刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:02:00.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　うまくいくとは限らない毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:02:00.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些有點小挫折的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:03.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:03.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你微笑面對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:06.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:06.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:14.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たったひとことがどれほど嬉しかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:14.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多麼令我開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:19.69,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとずっと覚えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:19.69,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至今日我也無法忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手鏈修好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 今天也一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 讓你擔心了對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大和談開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了麻美和愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們兩個在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘需要的時候我們絕對在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你要不要來攝影棚玩兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和讀者模特小亞美一起拍 我幫你介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很想見她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天和中西約好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦 惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 那我下次再找你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 小直 今天讀者模特小亞美跟我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像總是扔餌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她大概不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和她發生過什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛剛完全沒有看橘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠果然現在還是對大和…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 考試前都沒時間見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才一起學習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不是我 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好手鏈挺費力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你還是修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著它就感覺黑澤一直在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像它在對我說 你不是一個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一轉眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我想在這附近買點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以等你打完工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一會兒去K歌 你也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我想買點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要買什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個…就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不好意思什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給橘帶個好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛子 昨天謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了 告訴我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 愛子 說啦說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問啦 走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀小哥 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你總來照顧生意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…還有一個小時呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要這些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可以的話 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就開個玩笑 玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很喜歡樂園呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一問一下 你知道那個掛墜可以許願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許願?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道還帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 鑰匙旁邊那個圓環
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把願望寫在粉色絲帶上繫上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望就會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人帶著一對的 戀情就會持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你有男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼單純
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 梅 怎麼都沒跟我說過交男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這孩子太生分啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我當模特的時候 也讓梅等了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用往心裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼才好…應該很多話可說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有很多話想說 可這種時候反倒說不出了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才也在想同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎~又是一轉眼就到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅家如果超級遠就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單程要三天那麼遠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可傷腦筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來用烘乾機吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的襯衫濕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 我家沒有男人所以沒衣服給你換
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒…沒事 我又不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是流了奇怪的汗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉好紅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你這麼珍惜那手鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 不會壞的成對兒的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對戒 對戒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和黑澤成對的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還叫黑澤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實很早前就想叫大和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想你這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你叫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 大概是因…因為緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 可是早就想這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…大和的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 來幫我做飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏挑這個時候進來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種樣子…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係 舒服就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道歉沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過原來你就是梅的男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 他好像很為難哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子在家就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校會不會不合群？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…梅同學又堅強 又有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常尊重她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這麼誇張…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅同學不隨大流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有個性 卻又能為人著想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.07,0:13:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是第一次有人這麼誇她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從小就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為就我一個人這麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 哭出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棉花糖 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你與梅相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到媽媽那麼安心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了大和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛件上吊著的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是情侶對戒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和買給你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢梅 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是訂婚戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 真的太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊 那個咖啡店的老闆和事務所的經濟人還認識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說隨時可以去玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以直呼大和的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是下雨 或是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是寒風過境天氣轉涼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大和 還有朋友們 日復一日地度過著愉快的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是做夢都沒想到過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然也能有這樣的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海啊 竹村海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！竹村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你來辦公室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你男朋友是大和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒見 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽到過傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竹村同學是真要回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大和是一個中學的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到海會轉學回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還留了一級
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 或許他已經不這麼想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前跟你說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學的時候 最好的朋友成為被欺負的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然悄悄跟他說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人前卻什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來他就轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…說的就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他大變樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得這麼高大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說喜歡樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 梅你怎麼認識海的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他常光顧我打工的店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 我終於辦好轉學手續了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你認識大和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經是個受氣包的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說是 大和跟我說過他視而不見的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不拐彎抹角了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了向欺負過我的人報仇才回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此鍛煉身體 甚至留了級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是絕對不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是跟欺負你的人沒區別了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吃過的苦頭加注回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有什麼改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒被欺負過的人怎麼會懂我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有過啊 被欺負的經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最近才交上了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要用很多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望欺負過我的人 有一天會理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠改變的東西 我會用盡全力去改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌棄的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新產品 剛才才拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不怎麼愛吃甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是買甜麵包 我想你可能喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要報仇 我已經不是從前的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材比較高大 有威懾力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:20:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉上有痘痕 嘴角有痣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我做過的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起頭來 我要打回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 竹村
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒認出我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他連欺負過我的事情都忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就這麼一點價值麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我糾結至今的事情原來這麼可笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吃過的苦頭加注回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有什麼改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 去接女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是叫橘梅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能呢 喜歡橘梅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:02.40,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(978,493)}「各自不同的…」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:13.08,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\be3}慣れきた表情の　冷たい朝が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:13.08,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}喜歡能看到你熟悉表情的清冷早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:18.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}あからさまなった意図みせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:18.85,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}如此直率地向我表明心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:25.44,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}予言のような空の色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:25.44,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}天空的顏色如預言般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:30.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}そんなに意地悪しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:30.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}不要這樣的捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:36.75,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}笑った薄い唇に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:36.75,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}你的薄唇邊掛著微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:42.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}傾く影を追いかけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:42.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}我追尋著你傾斜的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:48.71,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}君さえもわからないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:48.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}即使我還對你一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:57.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}頼りない　もっと抱きしめて放題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:57.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}雖然不可靠 但請自由地擁抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:00.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}重ねていくいつもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:00.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}總會有許多的交匯處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:08.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}頼りないぐらい　不器用なslow dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:08.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}雖然不可靠 笨拙的slow dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:14.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}揺れる気持ちを乗るの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:14.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}但還是希望你能跟著搖曳的心一起走下去

Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在密室裡跟大和獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽正好回來了
